Text: Is this the PS1 game? I never play this game before but the only closest Pokemon like game I played in the old playstation is Jade Cocoon.
Yes, this is the ps1 version. It's already converted to PSP format. If you haven't, you should download it and try it out. Its a really good game. :)
Thanks. Is it anything like Dragon Warrior Monsters? Monster breeding and such?

Sort of, you can find eggs and hatch them then raise the monster but no interbreeding to make new monsters or anything. You can also upgrade the town like: adding a bowling alley (mini game) or a casino or library etc. you can also romance people in the game if you like.
Cool man. Thanks alot. Also All the games I torrented can no longer be seeded since i moved them all to a new folder For psp games. Is there a way that I can seed them from the new folder?

I am using Utorrent and I don't want to re-download it by changing the download location by right clicking it just to seed it. It kills the bandwidth but I want to seed because I know how annoying it is when people don't seed.
Ok delete the questions. I found out how to get it to seed now. I just need to right click and set download location. Select to view all files and just click on it and done.
